{"tid":1450682,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"以後別要只著黑色衫，紅橙黃綠青藍紫七彩什麼都著","createTime":"2019-08-11T17:49:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T15:33:33.000Z","uid":68306,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"245696bbc335c717fff99d949c19929e1cc65223","tid":1450682,"uid":68306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:49:28.000Z","msg":"今晚很多人被捕⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n看到警察暴力的打，心很痛⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n前面的，以後別要只著黑色衫，紅橙黃綠青藍紫七彩什麼都著，撇除了黑色的「標籤效應」。而且他們開始著黑色衫假扮示威者，別讓他們得逞。<br />\n<br />\n他們衝過來時，看情況掉帽掉口罩，有限錢，總好過被拉。掉帽掉口罩變回普通市民，別讓他們太容易分辨出來。<br />\n<br />\n我知道你們不怕死，但留著命更重要。<br />\n<br />\n就算死也要活下去。"},{"pid":"833d5ac8851c5ee3458548db0637cf8b6470f40f","tid":1450682,"uid":157626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:51:52.000Z","msg":"black bloc係用嚟保護前線保護自己<br />\n負評，上一頁"},{"pid":"a5c9e25656c7b92597041bd90b414d1ebfafee4e","tid":1450682,"uid":67425,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:32:38.000Z","msg":"樓主..你個腦去咗邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n除帽比警棍打？除帽就唔會比人打？<br />\n唔著黑色衫 就冇警犬扮示威者？"},{"pid":"d105331a035059ef4b9f1e982ab277aa16471fce","tid":1450682,"uid":67425,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:33:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主..你個腦去咗邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n除帽比警棍打？除帽就唔會比<span style=\"color: red;\">狗</span>打？<br />\n唔著黑色衫 就冇警犬扮示威者？</blockquote>"}]}